aces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會搞到好多人其實，不過條氣又唔順。<br />\n我黎打工唔係比人打。"},{"pid":"93d26209af86a267841f3c7eff25b3313ec5f451","tid":407810,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:56:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4432c8667cd3fae3014826dd300528ad3f3ed419","tid":407810,"uid":148851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即刻暈, 攞工傷, 再告佢傷人.</blockquote><br />\n等我下次即刻仆低，之後再屌7佢。"},{"pid":"15ea3713313325e78c8c9f132eeb1e23af01b4b6","tid":407810,"uid":148851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辣殺奴工</blockquote><br />\n不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個acc 特登為左呢年事開。"},{"pid":"430f1922cfe6041b3156d2e505ff5a733e8f64a1","tid":407810,"uid":59192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:58:12.000Z","msg":"大力打後尾枕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣打到變傻仔"},{"pid":"fd1daa9556b170bba5b3c7fc08e6371be6589363","tid":407810,"uid":148851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打返佢囉<br />\n一陣告又告唔入</blockquote><br />\n我打佢實一身蟻。個臭西同高層好撚fd"},{"pid":"34cc4d80e962e61a65227ed77167d5a1af1f8dfe","tid":407810,"uid":148851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大力打後尾枕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一陣打到變傻仔</blockquote><br />\n前幾日比佢打左下，差d痛到喊出黎。<br />\n屌佢老母我都有老母生架。"},{"pid":"dfad49514a448e096a6c5ed14c7e1529c96c18b5","tid":407810,"uid":62384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:00:06.000Z","msg":"搞大佢<br />\n一拍兩散"},{"pid":"13f0a023c1bb4763efbccf69b7f3b0bb9ccda92e","tid":407810,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T18:00:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03821c992a5bf30